C_WT.legacy_disclaimer:
21-inch wheels are equipped with low-profile performance tires that provide less protection from, and are consequently more likely to suffer damage from, uneven road surfaces, debris, curbs, and other common obstacles. Damage to wheels or tires from these conditions are not covered under the Model S new vehicle limited warranty. 21-inch wheels with low-profile performance tires reduce battery range compared to 19-inch wheels with all season tires. Model S does not come with a spare wheel and tire.

Low-profile performance tires are meant for summer use and will not have adequate traction in cold, snowy or icy conditions. We recommend driving on winter tires, available on both 21-inch and 19-inch wheels, in winter weather.
C_WT.name: Wheels

configSetLocale.gas_disclaimer:
Electric Vehicle Incentives Model S qualifies for electric vehicle incentives in British Columbia, Ontario and Quebec. Click here for additional information and visit the program’s website for important details on eligibility and availability. Gasoline Savings Electric vehicles are less expensive to fuel than gasoline powered vehicles. The average person drives between 15,000 and 25,000 kilometers and spends between $1,800 and $3,000 on gasoline per year. In comparison, the cost of electricity to power Model S over the same distance is five times lower. Over the five year average length of car ownership, that’s between $8,000 and $12,000 in gasoline savings.

We've assumed a fuel economy of 11.8 kilometers per liter for a comparable gasoline powered sedan. We’ve also assumed the national average of $0.12 per kilowatt hour for electricity, 10% charging on Tesla’s Supercharger network enabling free long distance travel and $1.23 per liter for premium gasoline over the next five years.
configSetLocale.incentives_txt: Incentives are available in Ontario ($8,500 CAD) and Quebec ($8,000 CAD).

Prices do not include license, insurance, registration, applicable taxes, levies, and fees or regionally required equipment, service, and charges. Range We provide detailed information about the range that you can expect with your Model S based on the options that you select and the way that you like to drive.Wheels There are different advantages to the 21-inch and 19-inch wheels. 本網站所示資料乃基於當時數據釐訂。假若設計、規格、價格及生產日期有所改動，恕不作另行通知，並僅適用於香港地區車輛。當你的車輛進入生產程序時，某些功能和選項可能不再適用。

21 吋與 19 吋車輪在不同路況上各有優點，例如 21 吋輪胎操控一般較佳；而 19 吋輪胎則較耐磨損，且在遇上障礙物或惡劣路面情況時保護性能較佳。
configSetPrices.gas_disclaimer:
電動車輛稅務及牌費優惠

電動車輛豁免首次登記稅，同時亦可每月節省達 $553 牌費。

已認可的核准公布零售價

如欲了解詳情，請透過此連結參閱Model S已認可的核准公布零售價。

節省燃料開支

相比傳統燃油汽車，電動車的燃料費用較為便宜。以平均每年行駛約 10,000 公里計算，一年的汽油開支約為 HK＄10,100；而 Model S 行駛同等里數所耗電力的只需其十分之一費用。以車輛平均五年換車周期計算，一共可節省約 HK $37,700。

以上計算假設同級內燃房車每 100 公里的耗油量約 7.2 公升，例如 2016 Mercedes E300；並假設未來五年平均優質油價為每公升 HK＄13.99 、平均電費每kWh為HK＄ 1.34，車主 30% 的時間使用Tesla Supercharger免費長途充電。

APE1.description:
升級版的 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛功能令你在原有優越的駕駛體驗上再添全新功能。是次升級包括從原有的一個鏡頭增加至四個以提高準確度及擴闊拍攝範圍，並探測到相鄰行車線上快速靠近的車輛。另外12個超聲波聲納感應器，可360度全方位覆蓋車輛四周，其探測距離和解析度是上一代感應器的兩倍。

新一代處理器的運算能力是上一代的40倍，用於處理顯著增加的感應器資訊。受惠於運算能力的提升，你的 Tesla 將能夠根據交通狀況調整速度，保持在行車線內行駛，甚至能在無需駕駛者人手控制的情況下進行自動變換行車線，或在高速公路間切換行駛，並在將抵達目的地時駛離高速公路，在接近停車位時自動停車，以及從車庫被「召喚」出來。雖然如此，升級版的 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛將繼續旨在用作輔助駕駛用途，駕駛者必須時刻保持對車輛的操控。

Tesla 升級版的 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛軟件預計在 2016 年 12 月完成測試，並將透過 OTA 更新供車輛下載；但正式軟件推送日期則視符當地法規認可而定。
APE1.disclaimer: 新車交付後升級需 HK$46,500
APE1.long_name: 升級版 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛
APE1.name: 升級版 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛

APF2.description:
升級版硬件包括主動攝像鏡頭，數量由四個增加至八個，令全自動駕駛功能能夠在大部份情況下使用；Tesla相信安全度相較於一般人手駕駛操控，至少提升近一倍。本系統的設計宗旨是讓車輛能夠在無須駕駛者採取任何動作下，都能行駛短程與長程旅程。對於已經啟用自動充電連接的Supercharger，你甚至不需要人手為車輛插入充電線。

你只需要輕鬆在出發點上車，然後指示車輛需要前往的目的地便可。如果你沒有作出任何指示，車輛將會檢視你的行事曆並按行事曆內容前往其預設目的地；而若行事曆沒有相關內容，則會設定你的住所視為目的地。你的 Tesla 更會計算出最佳路線，能夠在市區街道（即使沒有行車線）、設有交通燈的複雜十字路口，或在停車標誌位置、迴旋處和高速公路之間導航。當你抵達目的地後，在停車場門口下車後，你的車輛就會進入泊車搜尋模式，自動尋找泊車位置。當需要用車時，你只需在手機上點選便能夠「召喚」車輛。

請注意，自動駕駛功能的應用須通過大量因不同地域而不同的軟件合法性確認，並獲得當地法律、法規的許可。因此根據車輛所屬地區不同，上述各項功能元件能否在某地區實際推出並應用尚存不確定性，並將取決於所在地區的法律、法規許可情況。同時請注意，雖然你可以使用自動駕駛的Tesla車輛接送朋友和家人，但如果用於車輛共用、叫車服務等營利性服務，則須獲得“Tesla Network”的許可，相關細節將在明年公佈。
APF2.disclaimer: 新車交付後升級需 HK$31,000</br>須配備升級版的 Autopilot 自動輔助駕駛
APF2.name: 全自動駕駛功能

CF00.description:
Model S內置標準10kW充電裝置，每小時充電能保充大約50公里的行車距離。日常使用情況下，每晚以Tesla家用充電器Wall Connector或流動充電器Mobile Connector充電，已足夠為Model S完全重新充電。在進行長途駕駛時，Model S可使用不斷擴展的Supercharger網落在旅途中補充電量。

升級的15kW充電配置選擇，配合連接380V電源的Type 2牆上充電器使用時，可為Model S提升充電效能至每小時保充約75公里的行車距離。充電效率在使用Mobile Connector、CHAdeMO或Supercharger時則不受影響。
CF00.disclaimer: 新車交付後啟用需 HK$14,700
CF00.long_name: 高效充電配置（72amp充電裝置）
CF00.name: 高效充電配置（72amp充電裝置）

FG02.description: Cut through fog and illuminate obstacles on dark roads with LED fog lights that are controlled through the touchscreen. Our newly redesigned fog lights are designed to work with our LED cornering lights and headlights as a complete system.
FG02.name: Exterior Lighting Package

HP01.description: Designed to mimic the fluid, futuristic design of Model S, the 80 amp Wall Connector is the fastest, easiest way to charge at home. The 80 amp Wall Connector does not require Dual Chargers, but it will not reach its maximum 80 amp charging capability without them. This wall connector is under development and is expected to ship in late 2014.
HP01.name: 80 amp Wall Connector (Preorder)

IX01.description:
Wrap the interior of your car in the same luxurious Nappa leather used for our seats. Selectively chosen top-grade hides are minimally processed to retain their natural character. The result is an especially soft, smooth finish for the following surfaces:
  • Lower instrument panel
  • Armrests (door and console)
  • Driver airbag cover
IX01.name: Extended Nappa Leather Trim

LP01.description:
Add ambiance to Model S with strategically placed LED lights that illuminate without reflecting off the windshield. Interior lighting includes:
  • Door-panel ambient lights
  • Second-row footwell lights
  • Second-row puddle lights
LP01.name: Premium Interior Lighting

PI01.description:
• HEPA 高效微粒空氣過濾系統，過濾效率超出普通高級汽車過濾器達 100 倍，可過濾空氣中 99.97% 以上的污染微粒，並有效去除車艙內的過敏原、細菌及其他污染物。
    包括「生化武器防禦模式」
  • 兩個活性炭空氣過濾系統可防止氮氧化物、尾氣中的碳氫化合物，以及其他異味進入車廂
  • Performance 車輛若選配黑色或杏色 Tesla 豪華座椅，其前排透氣座椅可透過座椅表面的孔隙循環清涼乾爽的空氣。
  • 三個動態 LED 轉向燈，增強夜間能見度
  • LED 霧燈
  • 如選擇真皮座椅，將同時搭配真皮的扶手、方向盤以及儀錶盤下方的面板
  • Alcantara 儀錶盤綴飾
  • 柔和的 LED 車內氣氛燈
  • 發光車門把手
  • 電動掀尾車門
  • 快速連接電話座
PI01.name: 尊享升級組合

PS01.description: Add extra privacy to the cargo area with the removable parcel shelf, which slides between the rear seats and rear window to shield belongings from view.
PS01.name: Parcel Shelf

PX01.description: Performance Plus adds world class handling to the incredible acceleration of Model S Performance, while also improving range. After hundreds of iterations affecting every detail of the suspension, our vehicle dynamics team was able to achieve the rare outcome of improving both performance and efficiency. In addition to upgraded dampers, bushings, stabilizer bars and tires, the rear tires are 20 mm wider and staggered for improved acceleration on low grip surfaces. Range improves 10 to 20 kilometers over regular 21" wheels.
PX01.disclaimer: Requires 85 kWh Performance, Tech Package, Smart Air Suspension, and 21" Wheels
PX01.name: Performance Plus

SU01.description: 智能調節 Model S 的底盤高度，提高車輛的操控性能及效率，同時令駕駛體驗更為舒適。無論是行駛陡峭路段、乘客上下車輛或裝卸貨物等情況，都可以根據需要，利用觸控屏調節 Model S 的底盤升降。結合 GPS 位置檢測功能，Model S 還會記錄該地點位置，當車輛再次接近同一個地點時自動調節到相應的高度。
SU01.name: 智能氣壓懸掛

TP03.description:
Max out your Model S with a suite of power and lighting features.

  • Power liftgate
  • Electrochromatic, power folding and heated side mirrors
  • Lighted door handles
  • LED fog and cornering lights

TR01.description: Carry up to 7 passengers in Model S by adding seating for two children with rear facing seats. Engineered to far exceed federal safety standards, they attach to a second frame that augments our standard bumper with high strength aluminum for the utmost protection. These comfortable seats fold completely flat into the floor when not in use.
TR01.name: Rear Facing Seats
